{"tid":481881,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)熱爆MADAM 皇家特工1-2","createTime":"2017-11-27T14:57:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-27T20:35:30.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"442ea28a0b55b3fe4ba344c23f08dc408ba947f1","tid":481881,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T14:57:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=rnqslD%2FeyGi1jBXdHZI3pP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=905cf3bf\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=rnqslD%2FeyGi1jBXdHZI3pP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=0663be26\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得OKRU睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/b/bf/The_Heat_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fb%2Fbf%2FThe_Heat_poster.jpg&h=d675e178&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/8/8b/Kingsman_The_Secret_Service_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F8%2F8b%2FKingsman_The_Secret_Service_poster.jpg&h=fd1bb461&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/thumb/4/42/Kingsman_The_Golden_Circle_Poster.jpg/220px-Kingsman_The_Golden_Circle_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fthumb%2F4%2F42%2FKingsman_The_Golden_Circle_Poster.jpg%2F220px-Kingsman_The_Golden_Circle_Poster.jpg&h=3adf5e66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1精明細心的聯邦調查局女探員Sarah Ashburn接受上級委派的任務，到波士頓去抓捕大毒梟Simon Larkin，到之後與當地警察局一位辦事粗魯的女警員Shannon Mullins展開合作對付毒販，她倆在辦案過程中搞出了不少笑話。<br />\n<br />\n2.「金士曼」表面上是英國倫敦薩佛街上的一家裁縫店，天天為客戶量身打造帥氣的西服，實際上卻是一個歷史淵源久遠的民間諜報組織，以世界和平為宗旨，曾經多次打擊了嚴重犯罪，卻極為低調，不欲人知。但他們的能力卻不亞於英國秘密情報局（俗稱軍情六處，MI6）、美國中央情報局（CIA）、俄國對外情報局（FIS，原為KGB第一總局）、以色列情報特務局（MOSSAD）等知名的國家情治單位，<br />\n1997年「金士曼」的一群探員潛入位於中東的恐怖組織巢穴，順利逮捕其首腦，特務哈利&middot;哈特（代號加拉哈德，取自英國傳奇《圓桌武士》）審問首腦時，卻因一時失誤沒發現首腦想用手榴彈同歸於盡，導致一名探員用肉身阻擋而英勇犧牲，雖然救了其他人，但也讓哈特感到十分愧疚......<br />\n<br />\n3.一年前，伊格西&middot;安文率間諜組織「金士曼特務」挫敗里奇蒙&middot;范倫坦播送神經波廣播毀滅全人類的陰謀後，拿下師父哈利&middot;哈特的代號－「加拉哈德」，和瑞典皇室的提兒蒂公主在一起生活。一次回家路上，在瓦倫丁事件中丟掉手臂和聲帶的金士曼特務落選者查理&middot;赫斯基伏擊了伊格西。伊格西在倫敦的飆車大戰中躲避查理與他一眾手下的追殺，但查理切斷他的機械手臂，利用車子的電腦系統駭入金士曼的伺服器。伊格西出席瑞典皇室晚宴期間，金士曼的總部和所有特務（除了梅林外）的住宅都被飛彈摧毀，英國所有金士曼特務都被除掉<br />\n<br />\n11 30PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=rnqslD%2FeyGi1jBXdHZI3pP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=758dbeb3\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=rnqslD%2FeyGi1jBXdHZI3pP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=c3b4c40e\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d8b0f0c006de7f4f59b7f97c9a4435a2627c2fe","tid":481881,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T15:00:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=